@node "edit" "A guide to HYDRA"

To join the chart please contact:

           In Norway:        Trouble (SysOp: Into Exile!)

           In Denmark:       Mr.Hyde

other countries are welcome, but must establish a HQ first! it would be
impossible for the DK staff to manage other countries too! (and to danm
expensive!)


 A little note on how things work in Hydra!


:: THE CHARTS ::

 Each country in HYDRA will get a board chart with the 3 main catagories

      xTERNAL uPLOADS & aCTIVE cALLS
      oNLINE bYTES
      lOCAL uPLOAD & lEGAL vOTES

up to 20 boards will be allow in the charts! but ofcoz the HQ decides
how many they will count!

 Each country in HYDRA will get a trader chart, with as many traders we
can fit into the mag!

 Apart from this we might make a complete trader chart, with all the 
traders counted in their country charts, in one big chart!


:: THE VOTES ::

 After finished the counting tools, we're now planning on improving the 
vote section! but we have not decided anything yet!


:: A little note on LOCAL UPLOADING! ::

 A few SysOps have been arguing that they have not uploaded anything 
locally, yet the tools said they had... I'm sorry, but the tools makes a 
complete list of files not found in the UDLOGs, and I've not spotted a 
single error yet...


:: PLANS FOR THE FUTURE ::

